sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Client 1 (Admin)
    participant Mod as Client 2 (Mod)
    participant API as Go API (Controllers)
    participant SSE as SSE Broker
    participant DB as MySQL DB

    Note over Admin, Mod: 1. Clients establish persistent connection
    Admin->>SSE: GET /api/moderator/stream
    Mod->>SSE: GET /api/moderator/stream

    Note over Admin: 2. Admin performs a mutating action
    Admin->>API: POST /api/moderator/war-room/deploy
    API->>DB: Update Player's FightingAllianceID
    DB-->>API: Transaction Success

    Note over API, SSE: 3. API notifies the Broker
    API->>SSE: sseBroker.Notifier <- "REFRESH_WARROOM"

    Note over SSE, Mod: 4. Broker broadcasts to all connected clients
    SSE-->>Admin: Event stream message: "REFRESH_WARROOM"
    SSE-->>Mod: Event stream message: "REFRESH_WARROOM"

    Note over Admin, Mod: 5. LiveSyncManager intercepts & triggers refetch
    Admin->>API: Background GET /moderator/war-room/stats
    Mod->>API: Background GET /moderator/war-room/stats

    Note over Admin, Mod: UIs update seamlessly in real-time